\pard\nowidctlpar\sb100\sa100\kerning0\b0\fs24\par
"What?" Midge sputtered in disbelief. "Strathmore claims our data is wrong?"\par
Brinkerhoff nodded and hung up the phone.\par
"Strathmore \i denied\i0  that TRANSLTR's been stuck on one file for eighteen hours?"\par
"He was quite pleasant about the whole thing." Brinkerhoff beamed, pleased with himself for surviving the phone call. "He assured me TRANSLTR was working fine. Said it was breaking codes every six minutes even as we speak. Thanked me for checking up on him."\par
