"There's no way \i Greg Hale\i0  is Tankado's insurance! It's absurd! Tankado would never trust Hale."\par
"Commander," she said, "Hale sank us once before--Skipjack. Tankado trusted him."\par
Strathmore could not seem to find words.\par
