Strathmore held up his hand requesting a moment to think.\par
Susan looked nervously in the direction of the trapdoor. The opening was just out of sight behind TRANSLTR, but the reddish glow spilled out over the black tile like fire on ice. \i Come on, call Security, Commander! Abort TRANSLTR! Get us out of here!\i0\par
