\pard\nowidctlpar\sb100\sa100\kerning0\b0\fs24\par
"It's accelerating!" Soshi yelled from the back of the room. "It's the wrong code!"\par
Everyone stood in silent horror.\par
On the screen before them was the error message:\par
\pard\nowidctlpar\sb100\sa100\qc ILLEGAL ENTRY. NUMERIC FIELD ONLY.\par
\pard\nowidctlpar\sb100\sa100 "Damn it!" Jabba screamed. "Numeric \i only! \i0 We're looking for a goddamn number! We're fucked! This ring is shit!"\par
